title: 'tools_builtin.ml: shell command stdout streaming with ANSI preserved'
---
Add optional on_output_chunk callback to shell execution path. Use Lwt_process.open_process_full or Lwt_io for line streaming. Accumulate full output for ToolResult. Emit ToolOutputDelta per chunk. Preserve ANSI escape codes (don't strip them).